name: Frost Bite Hot Sauce
description: Frostbite Hot Sauce (5 FL.OZ. / 148 ml): The world's first white hot sauce. WARNING. Nothing frosty here. Extremely hot. Ingredients: Vinegar, Water, Salt, and Aquaresin of Capsicum. Add to beer, eggnog - anything you wanna' add some HEAT to!

name: Knox's Cracked Black Pepper Dry Rub
description: Knox's makes the best dry rubs which is why I sell more of his dry rub than any other brand I carry.  My personal favorite is his Cracked Black Pepper Dry Rub made with sea salt and toasted garlic and of course cracked black pepper.  This is the seasoning to give your steak or burger a leg up on the competition.  I never make a steak without it and that's why of all of my product line this dry rub makes the cut for the Facebook store!

name: Gator Hammock Wing Kit
description: This is a two-stage Ultimate Wing Kit from Gator Hammock.  This is literally the BEST SELLING WING SAUCE IN THE U.S. for a reason.  Sprinkle this Gator Hammock Seasoning on your chicken and then toss in this Gator Hammock Wing sauce for the ultimate Big Game party!  Loads of flavor and taste - NOT the typical neon orange wing sauce you find in your local grocery store.  Try it - you won't be disappointed.

name: Backdraft Fire Sauce
description: It sounds like it will burn your face off but trust me - it's not hot. This delicious condiment compliments virtually anything you eat.  I eat burgers with it, baked potatoes with it and my wife and I LOVE it on french fries.  Consider it a cross between a hot sauce and a mustard.  Tangy, a bit of heat, unique but nothing that will make you cry.  I ALWAYS have a bottle on hand... give it a shot.

name: 4-Pack Pyro Pete Sauces & Rubs 'ULTIMATE SALSA'
description: Our all-natural low sodium salsa is full of flavor. It starts out sweet and the comes the heat!  Fresh tomatoes, jalapenos, and other spices meld to make truly one of the freshest and best salsas on the market.  Taste why our salsa has been featured on the news TWICE!
